Squat Snatch
8 x 1+1+1 65-80%

Part 3-
Squat Clean
Hang Squat clean
Jerk
6 x 1+1+2 65-75%

Part 4-
6 min EMOM:
3 Clean DL+ 3 Clean Pull
75-85%
